'''Microwave''' radiation was a form of [[Radiation/Legends|radiation]] in the [[Spectrum/Legends|electromagnetic spectrum]]. Various machines such as [[microwave fermentation device]]s (used to ferment [[Deltron spice wine]]) and weapons such as [[microwave projector]]s utilized microwaves.

Some droids were equipped with [[microwave sensor]]s. [[I-5YQ]] had a [[microwave projector beam]] custom installed in him. The [[J9 worker drone/Legends|J9 worker drone]] contained a [[Torplex/Legends|Torplex]] microwave sensor.

